    {
      "id": "s10-102",
      "sectionId": "s10",
      "title": "写入文件",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": ":-- | --\n:-- | --\n`cat` | 用于显示文本文件内容，全部输出\n`EOF` | `end of file`，表示文本结束符"
    },
    {
      "id": "s10-103",
      "sectionId": "s10",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "cat > output.txt <<EOF\nthis is test eof\nthis is test eof2\nEOF"
    },
    {
      "id": "s10-104",
      "sectionId": "s10",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "输出 `cat output.txt`"
    },
    {
      "id": "s10-105",
      "sectionId": "s10",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "",
      "code": "this is test eof\nthis is test eof2"
    },
    {
      "id": "s10-106",
      "sectionId": "s10",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "追加内容"
    },
    {
      "id": "s10-107",
      "sectionId": "s10",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "cat >>2.txt <<EOF\n456\n789\nEOF"
    },
    {
      "id": "s10-108",
      "sectionId": "s10",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "`$` 等特殊字符时，须利用转义字符 `\\`"
    },
    {
      "id": "s10-109",
      "sectionId": "s10",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "cat > file <<EOF\nexport ORACLE_SID=yqpt \nexport PATH=\\$PATH:\\$ORACLE_HOME/bin  \nEOF"
    },
    {
      "id": "s10-110",
      "sectionId": "s10",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "取消变量替换，`EOF` 被加上双引号或者单引号，即可取消变量的替换"
    },
    {
      "id": "s10-111",
      "sectionId": "s10",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "cat%20%3C%3C%20%22EOF%22%20%3E%20output.sh%0Aecho%20%22This%20is%20output%22%0Aecho%20%241%0AEOF",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s10-112",
      "sectionId": "s10",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "所有TAB键将全部忽略[不能是空格]"
    },
    {
      "id": "s10-113",
      "sectionId": "s10",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "cat%20%3C%3C%20-EOF%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20echo%20%22This%20is%20output%22%0AEOF",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s10-114",
      "sectionId": "s10",
      "title": "特殊变量",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "表达式 | 描述\n:- | -\n`$?`       | 最后一个任务的退出状态\n`$!`       | 最后一个后台任务的 PID\n`$$`       | shell PID\n`$0`       | shell 脚本的文件名"
    },
    {
      "id": "s10-115",
      "sectionId": "s10",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "见[特殊参数](http://wiki.bash-hackers.org/syntax/shellvars#special_parameters_and_shell_variables)。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s10-116",
      "sectionId": "s10",
      "title": "%E5%8F%8D%E6%96%9C%E6%9D%A0%E8%BD%AC%E4%B9%89",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "%E2%80%A2%20%26nbsp%3B%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C!%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C%22%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C%23%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C%26%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C'%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C(%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C)%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C%2C%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C%3B%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C%3C%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C%3E%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C%5B%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C%7C%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C%5C%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C%5D%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C%5E%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C%7B%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C%7D%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C%60%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C%24%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C*%0A%E2%80%A2%20%5C%3F",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s10-117",
